race.comment: ICONIC GUESS (4) missed the frame last time but prior to that was an effortless Maiden winner (30.04) at this track, scoring by 2.75 lengths. Better than last run and makes appeal this time. RAMBO'S SHOUT (1) drew this same box last time when in the minors (31.12) in a Novice race over 520m at this track. Rates a key player. RUTHLESS ABBY (2) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (30.28) last time in a Novice race at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from six starts. Must be included in calculations. MERL'S LAD (6) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three spot most recently.
